TY  - JOUR
TI  - Investment Under Uncertainty
AU  - Lucas, Robert E.
AU  - Prescott, Edward C.
AB  - [This paper determines the time series behavior of investment, output, and prices in a competitive industry with a stochastic demand. It is shown, first, that the equilibrium development for the industry solves a particular dynamic programming problem (maximization of "consumer surplus"). This problem is then studied to determine the characteristics of the equilibrium paths.]
C1  - Full publication date: Sep., 1971
DB  - JSTOR
