TY  - JOUR
TI  - Some Statistical Models for Limited Dependent Variables with Application to the Demand for Durable Goods
AU  - Cragg, John G.
AB  - [Several models for limited dependent variables (variables having a non-negligible probability of exactly equaling zero) are examined. Estimation in and discrimination among the various models are considered, followed by a small sampling experiment into the procedures and an example of their application.]
